pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `Account` ( `AccountID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `CustomerID` int(11) NOT NULL, `FirstName` varchar(20) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `MidName` varchar(20) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `LastName` varchar(20) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `Address` varchar(60) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `State` varchar(2) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `Zipcode` int(5) NOT NULL, `Phone` varchar(15) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `City` varchar(45) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`AccountID`), UNIQUE KEY `CustomerID` (`CustomerID`), CONSTRAINT `Account_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`CustomerID`) REFERENCES `Customer` (`CustomerID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=22 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `Airplane` ( `AirplaneID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Name` varchar(15) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `First` int(11) NOT NULL, `Business` int(11) NOT NULL, `Econ` int(11) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`AirplaneID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=21 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `Arriveport` ( `ArriveID` varchar(10) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `City` varchar(45) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `Name` varchar(45) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `State` varchar(2) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`ArriveID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `Customer` ( `CustomerID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `UserName` varchar(12) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `Password` varchar(8) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `Email` varchar(30) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`CustomerID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=22 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `DepartPort` ( `DepartID` varchar(10) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `City` varchar(45) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `Name` varchar(45) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `State` varchar(2) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`DepartID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `Fare` ( `FareID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Amount` int(11) NOT NULL, `CardType` varchar(15) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `CardNum` int(11) NOT NULL, `CardOwner` varchar(45) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `Experation` date NOT NULL, `CVC` int(11) NOT NULL, `AccountID` int(11) NOT NULL, `FlightID` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`FareID`), KEY `AccountID` (`AccountID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=16 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `Flight` ( `FlightID` int(5) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `departID` varchar(10) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `arriveID` varchar(10) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `airline` varchar(20) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `AirplaneID` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `departTime` time DEFAULT NULL, `arriveTime` time DEFAULT NULL, `departDate` date DEFAULT NULL, `arriveDate` date NOT NULL, `EconomicPrice` int(5) NOT NULL, `BusinessPrice` int(5) NOT NULL, `FirsClassPrice` int(5) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`FlightID`), KEY `ArriveID` (`arriveID`,`departID`), KEY `DepartID` (`departID`), KEY `AirplaneID` (`AirplaneID`), CONSTRAINT `Flight_ibfk_4` FOREIGN KEY (`AirplaneID`) REFERENCES `Airplane` (`AirplaneID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=21 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `Passenger` ( `PassengerID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `FirstName` varchar(20) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `MidName` varchar(20) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `LastName` varchar(20) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `Age` varchar(1) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `Gender` varchar(1) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `BirthDate` date NOT NULL, `Class` varchar(1) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `AccountID` int(11) NOT NULL, `FlightID` int(11) NOT NULL, `SeatID` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `TicketID` varchar(5) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`PassengerID`), KEY `AccountID` (`AccountID`,`FlightID`), KEY `FlightID` (`FlightID`), KEY `SeatID` (`SeatID`), CONSTRAINT `Passenger_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`AccountID`) REFERENCES `Account` (`AccountID`), CONSTRAINT `Passenger_ibfk_2` FOREIGN KEY (`FlightID`) REFERENCES `Flight` (`FlightID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=25 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci COMMENT='1';

CREATE TABLE `Reserve` ( `ReserveID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `dateReserve` date NOT NULL, `ticketNo` varchar(8) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `AccountID` int(11) NOT NULL, `FareID` int(11) NOT NULL, `FlightID` int(11) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`ReserveID`), KEY `PassengerID` (`AccountID`,`FareID`), KEY `AccountID` (`AccountID`), KEY `FareID` (`FareID`), CONSTRAINT `Reserve_ibfk_2` FOREIGN KEY (`AccountID`) REFERENCES `Account` (`AccountID`), CONSTRAINT `Reserve_ibfk_3` FOREIGN KEY (`FareID`) REFERENCES `Fare` (`FareID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=16 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `Seat` ( `SeatID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `FlightID` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `classSeat` varchar(1) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `Row` char(1) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `selectSeat` int(11) NOT NULL, `Available` int(1) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`SeatID`), KEY `FlightID` (`FlightID`), CONSTRAINT `Seat_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`FlightID`) REFERENCES `Flight` (`FlightID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=1639 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;
